00:18:17.950 --> 00:18:27.440 align:middle line:90%


00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:31.290 align:middle line:84%
If many artists choose a
low-key and minimalist approach

00:18:31.290 --> 00:18:35.040 align:middle line:84%
to land art, be it in the
choice of raw materials, forms,

00:18:35.040 --> 00:18:39.330 align:middle line:84%
or representations, Stan Herd
creates more representational

00:18:39.330 --> 00:18:40.170 align:middle line:90%
earthworks.

00:18:40.170 --> 00:18:42.770 align:middle line:90%


00:18:42.770 --> 00:18:48.920 align:middle line:84%
>> From a very early age, I
began to look at what art was

00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:50.540 align:middle line:90%
out there in the world.

00:18:50.540 --> 00:18:55.190 align:middle line:84%
Certainly, Vincent van Gogh's
work jumped out as very unique.

00:18:55.190 --> 00:18:58.010 align:middle line:10%
