started to read his story,

00:18:58.010 --> 00:18:59.570 align:middle line:10%
then you really
start to understand

00:18:59.570 --> 00:19:02.120 align:middle line:10%
the soul of the artist.

00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:07.010 align:middle line:84%
Vincent lived it as no other
man did, in my opinion.

00:19:07.010 --> 00:19:10.220 align:middle line:84%
>> Stan paid tribute to the
man who inspired his art

00:19:10.220 --> 00:19:13.360 align:middle line:84%
by creating a large-scale
reproduction of Vincent van

00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:17.870 align:middle line:84%
Gogh's 1889 painting
