preparing to celebrate 500

00:21:25.380 --> 00:21:28.170 align:middle line:84%
years since the discovery
of America by Christopher

00:21:28.170 --> 00:21:30.532 align:middle line:90%
Columbus.

00:21:30.532 --> 00:21:32.990 align:middle line:84%
>> People in the country were
