00:22:07.420 --> 00:22:18.380 align:middle line:90%


00:22:18.380 --> 00:22:20.620 align:middle line:84%
I thought it might start
a dialogue for healing,

00:22:20.620 --> 00:22:25.330 align:middle line:84%
because really, if you
