00:32:52.285 --> 00:32:54.145 align:middle line:90%
[HEAVY BREATHING]

00:32:54.145 --> 00:32:55.295 align:middle line:90%
>> You sound exhausted.

00:32:55.295 --> 00:32:56.130 align:middle line:90%
>> Whoo!

00:32:56.130 --> 00:32:57.660 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, I'm getting
a bit tired now.

00:32:57.660 --> 00:33:00.262 align:middle line:90%


00:33:00.262 --> 00:33:01.062 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:33:01.062 --> 00:33:06.894 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:33:06.894 --> 00:33:13.220 align:middle line:90%


00:33:13.220 --> 00:33:14.930 align:middle line:84%
I mean, people
