00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:39.750 align:middle line:90%
I can see using my head torch.

00:33:39.750 --> 00:33:43.480 align:middle line:90%


00:33:43.480 --> 00:33:46.157 align:middle line:90%
It's fantastic this time of day.

00:33:46.157 --> 00:33:48.240 align:middle line:84%
The colors of the mountains
